text: Typhoon Gaemi, known as Super Typhoon Carina in the Philippines, was a very strong typhooon that affected the Philippines in early July 2024. It was the third named storm and third typhoon of the 2024 Pacific typhoon season. ==References== Category:2024 disasters in Asia Gaemi Gaemi Category:Typhoons in the Philippines Gaemi
title: Typhoon Gaemi
